## Retrieve Results

```typescript
for await (const result of await client.messages.batches.results(
  messageBatch.id,
)) {
  switch (result.result.type) {
    case "succeeded":
      console.log(
        `[${result.custom_id}] ${result.result.message.content[0].text.slice(0, 100)}`,
      );
      break;
    case "errored":
